UID:qZL_rzrFI_nxIqbwijT-W
SUMMARY:Cities In a Warming World: Urban Forest and Heat Islands
DTSTAMP:20260401T230751Z
DTSTART:20260716T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:This lecture series produced by Seward Park Audubon Center focu
	ses on urban forestry issues\, empowering participant with knowledge. This
	 series will focus on benefits of the urban tree canopy\, the history and 
	inequities of canopy cover\, and strategies to mitigate urban heat islands
	. Learn More Here\n\nhttps://rainierartscenter.org/events/cities-in-a-warm
	ing-world-urban-forest-and-heat-islands/
URL:https://rainierartscenter.org/events/cities-in-a-warming-world-urban-fo
	rest-and-heat-islands/
